recommendation.Strict-Transport-Security header is not: Strict-Transport-Security header is not set. It enforces secure connections and protects against MITM attacks.

recommendation.X-XSS-Protection header is not set. It e: X-XSS-Protection header is not set. It enables browser's built-in defenses against XSS attacks.

recommendation.Content-Security-Policy header is not se: Content-Security-Policy header is not set. It restricts resources the page can load and prevents XSS attacks.

recommendation.X-Frame-Options header is not set. It pr: X-Frame-Options header is not set. It prevents clickjacking attacks when set to 'deny' or 'sameorigin.

recommendation.X-Content-Type-Options header is not set: X-Content-Type-Options header is not set. It stops MIME type sniffing and mitigates content type attacks.

recommendation.Referrer-Policy header is not set. It co: Referrer-Policy header is not set. It controls referrer header sharing and enhances privacy and security.
